      "span_text": "In order to attack the problem of visualizing and detecting putative tRNA identity determinants and antideterminants with function logos and inverse function logos, we analyzed a dataset of 655 nonredundant inferred and actual tDNAs from bacteria called the Modified Sprinzl tRNA Database (MSDB) which also forms the basis of a recently introduced automated classifier of tRNA identity called TFAM  .",
